-- Philip Morris CR 2011 Net Revenue Excluding Taxes Rises 6.6%
-- B y   P e t e r   L a c a
-- 2012-03-27T06:30:41Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-27/philip-morris-cr-2011-net-revenue-excluding-taxes-rises-6-6-.html
Philip Morris CR (TABAK) , a unit of  Philip
Morris International Inc. (PM) , said full-year consolidated net
revenue excluding excise and the value-added taxes increased 6.6
percent to 12.2 billion koruna ($661.8 million).  Shipment volume declined 7.5 percent in the Czech Republic
and 2.8 percent in Slovakia, the company said in an e-mailed
statement in Prague today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Peter Laca in Prague at 
 placa@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Balazs Penz at 
 bpenz@bloomberg.net  